# This directory holds SQLx-managed migrations for Covalence Engine (018+).
#
# Migrations 001-017 were applied manually and are recorded in the
# _sqlx_migrations table via scripts/seed-sqlx-migrations.sh.
#
# New migrations must follow the SQLx naming convention:
#   {version}_{description}.sql
# where {version} is an integer greater than 17 (e.g. 018_add_tags.sql).
# SQLx will auto-apply unapplied migrations on engine startup.
